\begin_layout Section
Android sensors: Differences and comparison
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this project it was important to determine the user direction; the direction
 in which user is facing.
 Since the orientation of the phone relative to the user is unknown (a user
 may carry a phone in many ways), the problem of acquiring a user direction
 is not elementary.
 However, a sufficiently accurate user direction can be calculated using
 a combination of multiple sensors.
 
\end_layout

